o injury, but if fully recovered at Trials, the 18-year-old could soar to a spot on the team, or as an alternate.\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3058, \"end\": 3065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abraham_Lincoln\", \"score\": 0.9999999702008613, \"rank\": 2.9799165201390442e-08, \"text\": \"Lincoln\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abraham_Lincoln\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abraham_Lincoln\"}, {\"begin\": 3080, \"end\": 3089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Nationals\", \"score\": 0.9999993733801746, \"rank\": 5.792466854613553e-07, \"text\": \"Nationals\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Nationals\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Nationals\"}, {\"begin\": 3093, \"end\": 3103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Motor_Speedway\", \"score\": 0.9999999997667146, \"rank\": 2.317124570012346e-10, \"text\": \"Fort Worth\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Motor_Speedway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Motor_Speedway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also in the hunt isJoscelyn Roberson.The 18-year-old Texarkana native trains at World Champions Centre in Spring and brings down the house with her powerful tumbling.\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3392, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3279, \"end\": 3288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texarkana_metropolitan_area\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.170571945093702e-15, \"text\": \"Texarkana\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texarkana_metropolitan_area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texarkana_metropolitan_area\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She finished 10th in Fort Worth.\", \"from\": 3393, \"to\": 3425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3414, \"end\": 3424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Motor_Speedway\", \"score\": 0.9999999997667146, \"rank\": 2.317124570012346e-10, \"text\": \"Fort Worth\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Motor_Speedway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Motor_Speedway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the men's side, Tomball residentAsher Hongis eyeing a coveted spot in Paris, as is his Stanford University teammateColt Walkerof Cedar Park.\", \"from\": 3427, \"to\": 3570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3500, \"end\": 3505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.258245926593111e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3517, \"end\": 3536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_Cardinal\", \"score\": 0.9999306455706283, \"rank\": 6.632792409438602e-05, \"text\": \"Stanford University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_Cardinal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanford_Cardinal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fan favoriteFuzzy Benas, a Richmond native and University of Oklahoma standout, is also gunning for a spot.\", \"from\": 3571, \"to\": 3678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All the gymnasts vying for a spot on the Olympic team are:  Women  Men  Jordan Chiles, who trains in Spring, rocked a Beyonce-inspired leotard at Nationals to match her floor routine music.\", \"from\": 3680, \"to\": 3869, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3826, \"end\": 3835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Nationals\", \"score\": 0.9999993733801746, \"rank\": 5.792466854613553e-07, \"text\": \"Nationals\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Nationals\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Nationals\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"---  The story contains material from Associated Press and USA Gymnastics.It was updated with the news of Skye Blakely's injury on June 27.  it's about time  Houston sports fans finally have a way to watch their favorite teams without a cable or satellite subscription.\", \"from\": 3871, \"to\": 4140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3977, \"end\": 3989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skye_Blakely\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Skye Blakely\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skye_Blakely\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skye_Blakely\"}, {\"begin\": 4029, \"end\": 4036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"score\": 0.999839526317117, \"rank\": 0.0001604970877510137, \"text\": \"Houston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Launched Wednesday, December 3, the Space City Home Network's SCHN+ service allows consumers to watch the Houston Astros and Houston Rockets via iOS, Apple TV, Android, Amazon Fire TV, or web browser.\", \"from\": 4141, \"to\": 4341, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4177, \"end\": 4187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Space_City_(newspaper)\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Space City\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Space_City_(newspaper)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Space_City_(newspaper)\"}, {\"begin\": 4247, \"end\": 4261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Astros\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3169551330510166e-13, \"text\": \"Houston Astros\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Astros\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Astros\"}, {\"begin\": 4266, \"end\": 4281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Rockets\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.244487687776986e-52, \"text\": \"Houston Rockets\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Rockets\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Rockets\"}, {\"begin\": 4301, \"end\": 4308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Play\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.444420804454277e-15, \"text\": \"Android\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Play\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Play\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Available atSCHNPLUS.com, a subscription to SCHN+ allows sports fans to watch all Astros and Rockets games as well as behind-the-scenes features and other on-demand content.\", \"from\": 4343, \"to\": 4516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4425, \"end\": 4431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Astros\", \"score\": 0.9999016703421006, \"rank\": 9.833932587499975e-05, \"text\": \"Astros\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Astros\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Astros\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's priced at $19.99 per month or $199.99 annually (plus tax).\", \"from\": 4517, \"to\": 4580, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"People who watch Space City Network Network via their existing cable or satellite service will be able to access SCHN+ at no additional charge.\", \"from\": 4581, \"to\": 4724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4598, \"end\": 4608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Space_City_(newspaper)\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Space City\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Space_City_(newspaper)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Space_City_(newspaper)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the Houston Chroniclenotes, the Astros and Rockets were the only MLB and NBA teams not to offer a direct-to-consumer streaming option.\", \"from\": 4728, \"to\": 4865, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4735, \"end\": 4742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"score\": 0.999839526317117, \"rank\": 0.0001604970877510137, \"text\": \"Houston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\"}, {\"begin\": 4763, \"end\": 4769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Astros\", \"score\": 0.9999016703421006, \"rank\": 9.833932587499975e-05, \"text\": \"Astros\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Astros\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Astros\"}, {\"begin\": 4796, \"end\": 4799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MLB_Network\", \"score\": 0.9999256874344596, \"rank\": 6.889925931978989e-05, \"text\": \"MLB\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MLB_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MLB_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 4804, \"end\": 4807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.65810350302824e-20, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are thrilled to offer another great option to ensure fans have access to watch games, and the SCHN+ streaming app makes it easier than ever to cheer on the Rockets,\\\" Rockets alternate governor Patrick Fertitta said in a statement.\", \"from\": 4867, \"to\": 5101, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5064, \"end\": 5071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danica_Patrick\", \"score\": 0.9995763822881887, \"rank\": 0.00042377520080170197, \"text\": \"Patrick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danica_Patrick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Danica_Patrick\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Providing fans with a convenient way to watch their favorite teams, along with our network's award-winning programming, was an essential addition.\", \"from\": 5102, \"to\": 5249, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This season feels special, and we are committed to exploring new ways to elevate our broadcasts for Rockets fans to enjoy.\\\"\", \"from\": 5250, \"to\": 5373, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Astros owner Jim Crane echoed Feritta's comments, adding, \\\"Providing fans options on how they view our games is important as we continue to grow the game - we want to make it accessible to as large an audience as possible.\", \"from\": 5375, \"to\": 5597, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5375, \"end\": 5381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Astros\", \"score\": 0.9999016703421006, \"rank\": 9.833932587499975e-05, \"text\": \"Astros\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Astros\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Astros\"}, {\"begin\": 5388, \"end\": 5397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jim_Crane\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jim Crane\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jim_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jim_Crane\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are looking forward to the 2026 season and more Astros fans watching our players compete for another championship.\\\"\", \"from\": 5598, \"to\": 5716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5649, \"end\": 5655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Astros\", \"score\": 0.9999016703421006, \"rank\": 9.833932587499975e-05, \"text\": \"Astros\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Astros\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston_Astros\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SCHN+ is available to customers in Texas, Louisiana, Arkansas, Oklahoma and the following counties in New Mexico: Dona Ana, Eddy, Lea, Chaves, Roosevelt, Curry, Quay, Union and Debaca.\", \"from\": 5720, \"to\": 5904, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5755, \"end\": 5760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"score\": 0.9273569266470366, \"rank\": 0.07830762471913108, \"text\": \"Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas\"}, {\"begin\": 5762, \"end\": 5771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louisiana\", \"score\": 0.9992705299655409, \"rank\": 0.0007300025493115776, \"text\": \"Louisiana\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louisiana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louisiana\"}, {\"begin\": 5773, \"end\": 5781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Arkansas\", \"score\": 0.6948252337882701, \"rank\": 0.25268924489858524, \"text\": \"Arkansas\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Arkansas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Arkansas\"}, {\"begin\": 5783, \"end\": 5791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oklahoma_Sooners_football\", \"score\": 0.9088805664963656, \"rank\": 0.0906349328466917, \"text\": \"Oklahoma\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oklahoma_Sooners_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oklahoma_Sooners_football\"}, {\"begin\": 5822, \"end\": 5832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9999999053425244, \"rank\": 8.910946774408323e-08, \"text\": \"New Mexico\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Mexico\"}, {\"begin\": 5834, \"end\": 5842, \"title\":